* ===================================
* 題解
  * 蟬語 是 謝宇恆 設計的程序語言
    它的名字 來源與曹植的 蟬賦
      實淡泊而寡欲兮 獨咍樂而長吟
      聲噭噭而彌厲兮 似貞士之介心
  * 它以 小蟬語 爲基礎 而寫成
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/blob/master/README-cicada-nymph
* 瞭解更多
  * 你可以在這裏找到更多的文檔
    http://the-little-language-designer.github.io/cicada/intro/contents.html
* 最新版本
  * 這個程序的源代碼可以在這裏下載
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada
* 貢獻
  * 聊天
    用 IRC
    在 irc.freenode.net 服務器的 #cicada-language 頻道
  * 郵件列表
    用 google group
    論壇在這裏
    https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/cicada-language
  * 分享你的主意和經驗
    你可以編輯維基頁面
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/wiki
  * 發現錯誤 或 要求新性狀
    你可以在這裏創建話題
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/issues
  * 修復錯誤 或 貢獻新的性狀
    你可以在這裏要求我把你的貢獻狀融合到主要文庫中
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/pulls
* ===================================
* to explain the title
  * the name cicada-language comes from
    the cicada rhapsody of
    the ancient Chinese prince CAO Zhi
  * it is based on cicada-nymph
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/blob/master/README-cicada-nymph
* to learn more
  * you can find documentations here
    http://the-little-language-designer.github.io/cicada/intro/contents.html
* to get the newest version of the program
  * the source code of this program can be downloaded from
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada
* to contribute
  * to chat
    we use IRC
    we have #cicada-language channel on irc.freenode.net
  * mailing list
    we use google group
    you can find cicada-language forum here
    https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/cicada-language
  * to share your ideas and experiences
    you can edit the wiki page here
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/wiki
  * to track bugs, feature requests, and more
    you can create an issue here
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/issues
  * to send patch and fix bug
    you can do pull request here
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/pulls
* ===================================